name: Scorpio
description: Scorpio is the eighth star of the zodiac list. This star is in the order of 210-240 of the zodiac, between 207.25 and 234.75 degrees of celestial longitude. Under the tropical zodiac, the sun transits this area on average between October 23 to November 22, and under the sidereal zodiac, the sun transits the constellation Scorpius from about November 16 to December 15.
